#How to use

1. Create domains
	1.1 With specifying domain name and role
		$./create.sh {DOM_NAME} {DOM_ROLE}

	1.2 Without specifying domain name
		$./create.sh (This will create a random domain name with default role)

2. Remove domains
NOTE: This is not "xl destroy" which destroys domains running on Xen. 
So you should destroy domains with "xl destroy" first then remove domains.

	2.1 Remove a specific domain
		$./remove.sh {DOM_NAME}

	2.2 Remove all domains
		$./remove.sh all

3. List domains
	3.1 ./list.s
